data.description: Very nice home with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2 car garage. Living room, dining area, indoor laundry, and tile floors throughout. Available now. North Merced. 7 minutes to UC Merced's downtown campus center. Walking distance to Fahrens Park and Disc Golf course. Close to the dog park, and Merced's Apple Gate Park Zoo. Many stores and restaurants close by.
